column5: Hi all, took my boy down to the creek today to watch the suckers doing their 'THANG'.Took some underwater footage of the yearly dance.Cool to see.SUCKERS DOIN' THEIR THANG(Now with music)
I thought so too Terry.  I know you have a gopro too, pretty neat little gizmos eh?  have been dying to try it underwater, but had to wait for ages as the sucker run is sooooooo late this year.
Fish porn, for real! Just missing the cheesy music.
~~~~~AAAAH Phish Porn, who has the tissue
Bow chicka wow wow!!  Cool video Simon, which model GoPro do you have?
the Gopro really is handy in a lot of situations, no need for waterproofing ... neat to see how they don't seem to expend a lot of energy in the current
With that real cold water Simon. Thats the best time to catch an eat them. They aint that bad. Give it a try.  Did anyone catch the three some ?

CHEESY MUSIC ADDED!       SICK!      LOL...Hero 3 Black Edition.....what a pain in the arse it has been....really buggy....loads of issues....no battery life....freezes up.......finally the firmware update seems to have solved some of the issues.....but now it gets too hot to touch.....not good for my very expensive 64gb Class 10 sd card.       Yup....it has its own waterproof case, i need to work out how to mount it somewhere in the boat.       I think i'll stick to walleye and trout ....but might get a couple next year for the smoker...heard they aint bad.
Back to private are you Simon?
Sorry Roy, new mac computer lets me export straight from vid editing software....it always exports to Youtube with 'private' as default....should be watchable now
